OL,3,C'Missed opportunity' in care of
OL,4,Cprisoner who took his own life
OL,6,FAn inmate at Leeds Prison who took his
OL,7,Fown life did not receive a good enough
OL,8,Fstandard of mental health care, an
OL,9,Finvestigation has found.
OL,11,FAkash Akeel, 28, from Bradford, was
OL,12,Ffound dead in his cell on 31 December
OL,13,F2022. An inquest concluded that he had
OL,14,Ftaken his own life.
OL,16,FAn investigation by the Prisons
OL,17,FOmbudsman found that there was a
OL,18,Fmissed opportunity to assess Akeel's
OL,19,Frisk of suicide when he asked for
OL,20,Fantidepressant medication six weeks
OL,21,Fbefore his death.
