OL,3,C'Missed opportunity' in care of
OL,4,Cprisoner who took his own life
OL,6,FHealthcare staff prescribed
OL,7,Fantidepressants but failed to monitor
OL,8,Fthat Akeel was taking them. He had not
OL,9,Fcollected any of his antidepressant
OL,10,Fmedication by the time he died.
OL,12,FAkash had been remanded into custody
OL,13,Fat HMP Leeds on October 27, 2022,
OL,14,Fcharged with attempted burglary,
OL,15,Fstalking and harassment. He had been
OL,16,Fin prison many times before. The
OL,17,Falleged offences were against his ex-
OL,18,Fpartner who had a restraining order in
OL,19,Fplace against him.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
