OL,3,C'Missed opportunity' in care of
OL,4,Cprisoner who took his own life
OL,6,FThe Ombudsman said that there was no
OL,7,Findication that Akeel was at imminent
OL,8,Frisk of suicide when he died, however,
OL,9,Fopportunities were missed to assess
OL,10,Fhis mental health.
OL,12,FThe report from the Ombudsman said:
OL,13,F"The nurse who prescribed Mr Akeel's
OL,14,Fantidepressant medication did not do a
OL,15,Fmental health referral as she should
OL,16,Fhave done. The clinical reviewer
OL,17,Fconsidered that an assessment tool
OL,18,Fshould have been used to risk assess
OL,19,FMr Akeel given his history of mental
OL,20,Fhealth issues.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
