OL,3,C'Missed opportunity' in care of
OL,4,Cprisoner who took his own life
OL,6,FIt added: "Mr Akeel had not collected
OL,7,Fany of his antidepressant medication
OL,8,Fby the time he died. Staff failed to
OL,9,Ffollow this up when a pharmacy
OL,10,Ftechnician noticed it on 16 December.
OL,11,FThey again failed to follow it up
OL,12,Fproperly when it became apparent
OL,13,Fduring a medication review.
OL,15,F"The clinical reviewer concluded that
OL,16,FMr Akeel's mental healthcare was not
OL,17,Fequivalent to that which he could have
OL,18,Fexpected to receive in the community."
