OL,3,C'Missed opportunity' in care of
OL,4,Cprisoner who took his own life
OL,6,FPrison reception staff noted a history
OL,7,Fof suicide attempts and self-harm and
OL,8,Fdiscussed this with Akeel. He said
OL,9,Fthat he had not tried to harm himself
OL,10,Ffor a long time and had no current
OL,11,Fthoughts of suicide or self-harm.
OL,13,FITV News has contacted the Ministry of
OL,14,FJustice for a response to the report's
OL,15,Ffindings.
